{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a first-person simulation game where you run a retail company.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand your humble store into a huge retail company. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/Store01_3.gif?t=1738428298\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Store Workflow</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sign contracts with leading brands, order new products with an in-game computer, unpack the boxes, place the products into your store, and set the prices for your products.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Consider the market prices while setting up your product prices in the store for customer satisfaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/Contract01.gif?t=1738428298\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Products</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please make sure your customers find all their needs in the store.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Always expand your product portfolio and satisfy your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shirts, jackets, pants, sweatshirts, dresses, t-shirts, shoes, hats, and more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be aware of the market prices and purchase more products when they're cheap.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/ShelfFill03_1.gif?t=1738428298\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Place a sufficient number of checkouts and fitting rooms to reduce the waiting time for customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scan products and collect payments whether in cash or with card purchases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/Checkout01_1.gif?t=1738428298\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Expansions and New Teammates</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand your store and warehouse by leveling up your store and budget.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hire stockers to fill the racks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase more cash registers and hire new cashiers to minimize long queues at the checkouts and to reduce waiting time for customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/Cashier01.gif?t=1738428298\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Store Name","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3089130/c326dc96b34d7e3610b25598f6b83f09b46f26b2.jpg"},{"name":"Contracts","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3089130/3f2672acbd726c28036f066bd2c91aefe2014c0d.jpg"},{"name":"First Order","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3089130/a6ac2c187e78129174c43125239bab6d71051d91.jpg"},{"name":"Set Price","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3089130/6299f3f8b75719481a1e4e40fe7b1da770165eb2.jpg"},{"name":"Open the store","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3089130/5a22351d29348c973743c8d142f9fe1b8d99c5e1.jpg"},{"name":"First Checkout","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3089130/bcbb90b46d384a545050b9cf445b62e7c1c49d0d.jpg"},{"name":"First day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3089130/c882e66108faefcca6270e260ba2be10a8fe55cb.jpg"},{"name":"Workers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3089130/120e9a76baefc4fe46168b31195f819856f3fdf7.jpg"},{"name":"Expansion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/st